Package: lighttpd
Architecture: any
Provides:
 httpd,
 httpd-cgi,
 ${lighttpd:ModuleProvides},
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 media-types | mime-support,
 systemd-sysv | lsb-base,
Pre-Depends:
 ${misc:Pre-Depends},
Conflicts:
 lighttpd-mod-geoip,
 lighttpd-mod-trigger-b4-dl,
Recommends:
 spawn-fcgi,
 perl:any,
 lighttpd-mod-deflate,
 lighttpd-mod-openssl,
Suggests:
 openssl,
 php-cgi,
 php-fpm (>= 2:7.4),
 apache2-utils,
 lighttpd-doc,
 lighttpd-mod-webdav,
 lighttpd-modules-dbi,
 lighttpd-modules-lua,
Description: fast webserver with minimal memory footprint
 lighttpd is a small webserver and fast webserver developed with
 security in mind and a lot of features.
 It has support for
   * CGI, FastCGI and SSI
   * virtual hosts
   * URL rewriting
   * authentication (plain files, htpasswd, LDAP)
   * transparent content compression
   * conditional configuration
   * HTTP proxying
 and configuration is straight-forward and easy.

